item.title: The Revolving Fund
item.description:
The Revolving Fund

This video was produced by the National Trust for Historic Preservation and the 1772 Foundation. Created by the Savannah College of Art and Design it is a piece of enhanced content for the Fall 2014 issue of Forum Journal "Get Real about Real Estate."

item.title: An Appalachian Tale - Thesis Version
item.description:
An Appalachian Tale - Thesis Version

An Appalachian Tale was a one-man, thirteen day MFA thesis production filmed on location in the mountains of Pennsylvania - one man with the assistance of numerous individuals working for businesses, government agencies, and non-profit groups.
